    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the tomato<strong> </strong>sauce<strong> </strong>with your <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>and drizzle the chicken with <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and put the dish in the oven for an initial 12 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
