            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potatoes are cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> pepperoni </strong>finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2116.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
