    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>cheesy pepperoni chicken</strong> from the dish and give the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> a good mix up</p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy pepperoni chicken</strong> over the<strong> tomato sauce</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
